HEADWORD: Demivolt
<hw>Dem"i*volt`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F. <ets>demi-
volte</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Man.)</fld> <def>A half vault; one of the
